{"tid":1160630,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"香港有幾成人以廣東話為母語？","createTime":"2019-05-18T15:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-18T15:25:41.000Z","uid":142025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9b5bedabe10559141991bb28c139e9ffdc4f8f44","tid":1160630,"uid":142025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-18T15:22:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">統計處：</span></span><br />\n根據2015年統計處的調查數據，本港6至65歲人士，<span style=\"color: red;\">88.1%的母語為廣州話，3.9%為普通話</span>，3.7%為其他中國方言，1.4%為英語及餘下的2.8%為其他語言。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qt58JmV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQt58JmV.jpg&h=3c2968b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180505/20382122\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20382122&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2flT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=4ff66aa2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180505%2F20382122&h=1ad29df7\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180505/20382122</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/fd.jsp?file=B11302592016XXXXB0100.pdf&amp;product_id=C0000086&amp;lang=2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.censtatd.gov.hk%2Ffd.jsp%3Ffile%3DB11302592016XXXXB0100.pdf%26product_id%3DC0000086%26lang%3D2&d=vM7vEUXlfhstYrouAjV2flT2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=058a7806\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.censtatd.gov.hk/fd.jsp?file=B11302592016XXXXB0100.pdf&amp;product_id=C0000086&amp;lang=2</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">考評局：</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今年約5萬名中文科考生中，逾2000人以普通話應考，佔整體約4%</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NRPp09b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNRPp